org.archive.wayback.resourceindex.cdxserver

Class AccessCheckFilter.CDXSearchResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.archive.wayback.core.SearchResult
      • org.archive.wayback.core.CaptureSearchResult
        • org.archive.wayback.core.FastCaptureSearchResult
          • org.archive.wayback.resourceindex.cdxserver.AccessCheckFilter.CDXSearchResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Capture
    Enclosing class:
    AccessCheckFilter

    protected static class AccessCheckFilter.CDXSearchResult
extends FastCaptureSearchResult
    Adapts CDXLine to CaptureSearchResult interface. Fetches originalUrl, captureTimestamp and robotFlags from the CDXLine adopted (minimum required for known existing filter implementations). It also have setRobotFlag call modify robotflags field in the underlining CDXLine (necessary for soft-block feature).

    TODO: Unfortunately this is not as lightweight as it should have been. Only if CaptureSearchResult was an interface.

    Caveat: it only overrides those methods used by known existing filter implementations.

    See Also:
    CustomPolicyOracleFilter
